reviewText: Show started off great, but season 4 & 5 just went into a tailspin into weirdness, and the entire show devolved into a character spotlight on Captain Hunt and the story derailed into nonsense.
I think the writers were high.
Loved watching it!  It was a lot of fun with a complete story for each episode.  A lot like the original Star Trek with the same kind of humor.
please keep them comeing . great seasons
